org.glassfish.tyrus.websockets

Interface WebSocketListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    TyrusEndpoint, WebSocketApplication

    public interface WebSocketListener
    Interface to allow notification of events occurring on specific WebSocket instances.
    Author:
    Alexey Stashok, Pavel Bucek (pavel.bucek at oracle.com)

      • onClose

        void onClose(WebSocket socket,
           ClosingFrame frame)

        Invoked when WebSocket.onClose(org.glassfish.tyrus.websockets.draft06.ClosingFrame) has been called on a particular WebSocket instance.

        Parameters:
        socket - the WebSocket being closed.
        frame - the closing DataFrame sent by the remote end-point.
